our entire life, time, abilities, body, and material possessions to Him. #Shorts​​​​​​​​​​​​​​ #YouTubeShorts​​​​​​​​​​​​​​ 

Listen to Pastor Ted Wilson’s message about stewardship and what the Bible teaches about it.
